# Local Worker dev secrets. Copy to .dev.vars (git-ignored) for `npx wrangler dev`.
# In production these are set with `npx wrangler secret put <NAME>` — never commit real keys.

# xAI / Grok — https://console.x.ai  (Create API key)
XAI_API_KEY=xai-...

# Deepgram — https://console.deepgram.com  (API Keys → Create, Member role or higher)
DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=...
